			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">小鸭<br/><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="12" color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span></p>
