		</Group>
		<RichText x="66" y="800" width="498" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffbf">(N3) <span color="#ffffff">入战一段时间后进入「歼灭模式」，期间将召唤5只</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">冲鸭机关</span><span color="#ffffff">，持续40s；受到冲鸭机关的反撞攻击会使其损失</span><span color="#ffdfbf">5%生命值</span><span color="#ffffff">，破坏全部的冲鸭机关会令其瘫痪12s，期间抗性</span><span color="#ffdfbf">降至-50%</span><span color="#ffffff">。<br/></span><span>(N4) </span><span color="#ffffff">开局秒进入「歼灭模式」，持续67s，击破后瘫痪12s。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span color="#ffffff">开局秒进入「歼灭模式」，持续60s，击破后瘫痪12s。冲鸭机关的反撞攻击的伤害变为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20%冲鸭机关所受伤害</span><span color="#ffffff">。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="954" width="505" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">由「歼灭模式」召唤，一共5只，每只为<span color="#ffdfbf">25%大鸭生命值</span><span>，有100感电充能条，每次受到</span><span color="#ffacff">(月)感电反应伤害</span><span>积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">10</span><span>，攒满后反撞大鸭；期间小鸭受到的</span><span color="#ffacff">感电/月感电</span><span>伤害提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">150%</span><span>。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>感电条上限为200。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/摧枯之役-重拳出击鸭%B7重甲武库.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1166" y="847" blendMode="normal">
